libportage
------------------------------------------
LibPortage is a fast and portable library offering functionality for doing
package management in a Gentoo system. This includes ebuilds, binpkgs and
managing a portage-compatible configuration. The library will provide all the
functions one may need to write a drop-in replacement for Portage in C.

As a side effect of our effort to implement all portage features, there are
also a few documents we (the developers) wrote for ourselves to cover some of
Gentoo's internals which might be useful for external devs as well.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.0.1-1
  libarchive13-3.1.2-2
  libportage-devel-0.1_alpha0-1bl1
  libportage0-0.1_alpha0-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-1
  cygport-0.18.1-1
  gcc-core-4.9.2-3
  libtool-2.4.6-1
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/psychoschlumpf/libportage

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/psychoschlumpf/libportage/archive/v0.1_alpha0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libportage-0.1_alpha0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libportage-0.1_alpha0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libportage-0.1_alpha0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libportage-0.1_alpha0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libportage0-0.1_alpha0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libportage-devel-0.1_alpha0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libportage)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libportage.README
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/README
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/TODO
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/xpak.html
  /usr/share/doc/libportage/xpak.txt

(libportage0)
  /usr/bin/cygportage-0.dll

(libportage-devel)
  /usr/include/libportage/archives.h
  /usr/include/libportage/atom.h
  /usr/include/libportage/util.h
  /usr/include/libportage/version.h
  /usr/include/libportage/xpak.h
  /usr/lib/libportage.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libportage.pc

